Package: kataegis
Type: Package
Title: Kataegis: an R package to define and visualize the kataegis regions in cancer genomes
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Xue Lin, Jian Li
Maintainer: Xue Lin <xue.lin@njmu.edu.cn>
Description: The Kataegis program provide a convenient tool to define the 
    Kataegis region in cancer samples. The name Kataegis is a greek word meaning 
    storm, which is a vivid metaphor for the hypermutations occur in cancer genomes.
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
Suggests: knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews: VariantAnnotation, DataImport, Visualization
Imports: grDevices, graphics, stats, utils
